        <h1 class="definition-title">Exclusion</h1>
        <p class="definition-short">The humane method of removing comfort emergencies by allowing them to exit through one-way devices while preventing re-entry. This is the industry-standard, legally required approach for HVAC Repair.</p>
      </div>
